subtitles.text: Welcome to our IELTS vocabulary lesson!
Today we will learn advanced academic vocabulary.
First word is 'abundant' meaning plentiful or rich.
Example: The region has abundant natural resources.
Example: We need a comprehensive study plan.
Example: Please elaborate on your proposal.
Example: Education is fundamental to society.
Example: This represents a significant change.
These words are essential for IELTS success.
Practice using them in your writing and speaking.
Thank you for studying IELTS vocabulary with us!
